    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1922-07-15T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1922-07-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="237"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d237">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">723.2515/993</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Peruvian Ambassador</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Pezet</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-07-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 15, 1922</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Dear Mr. Secretary</hi>: I have been requested by Dr.
                    Porras to ask you to appoint a time on Monday next, July 17th when you could
                    receive him together with Dr. Aldunate of the Chilean Delegation; it having been
                    arranged between both Delegations at their last Joint <pb facs="0621" n="501"
                        xml:id="pg_501"/> Session that they would appeal to you for advise on
                    certain points on which they could not agree.</p>
                <p>With my expression [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">F. A. Pezet</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
